    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>BrickRobo Shop Simulator</i> allows you to take charge of your own brick store, managing inventory, setting prices, and serving customers to grow your business. Sell a variety of bricks and use collected bricks to customize and strengthen your <strong>BrickRobos</strong>. The stronger your robots, the more valuable they become! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/c9e4cec5c58dc5d7b789b832c1e7b660.poster.avif?t=1763694726\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/c9e4cec5c58dc5d7b789b832c1e7b660.webm?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/c9e4cec5c58dc5d7b789b832c1e7b660.mp4?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stock your store with various bricks and adjust pricing to attract customers while maximizing earnings. Keep shelves filled with in-demand bricks, experiment with pricing strategies, and optimize your sales to grow your business. A well-managed store leads to higher profits and better opportunities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/032cde76a8ea807c913f6e623c81d68a.poster.avif?t=1763694726\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/032cde76a8ea807c913f6e623c81d68a.webm?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/032cde76a8ea807c913f6e623c81d68a.mp4?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock <strong>Brick Packs</strong> to obtain a set of bricks in a specific size category, each pack containing multiple shapes but all in the same color. Carefully manage your packs to collect the right bricks needed for your <strong>BrickRobo</strong> customizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/d5327642345209005da920ba9bd6af4a.poster.avif?t=1763694726\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/d5327642345209005da920ba9bd6af4a.webm?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/d5327642345209005da920ba9bd6af4a.mp4?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect bricks and assemble your BrickRobo in the workshop. Experiment with different parts, adjust the design, and create a robot that suits your style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/eff69b967a09d2e6b0cc3c5eafbd5198.poster.avif?t=1763694726\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/eff69b967a09d2e6b0cc3c5eafbd5198.webm?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294640/extras/eff69b967a09d2e6b0cc3c5eafbd5198.mp4?t=1763694726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After customizing your <strong>BrickRobo</strong>, take it around the city and meet trainers eager for a challenge. Engage in strategic duels where your robot’s design and upgrades determine the outcome. Win battles to earn valuable rewards and refine your <strong>BrickRobo</strong> into an even stronger competitor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BrickRobo Shop Simulator offers a unique blend of business management and creative robot customization, making it the perfect experience for brick and robot enthusiasts alike. Start your journey today and build the ultimate store for BrickRobo fans!</p>",
